Visit your Insights Page: If you have NOT placed this widget in the Page Profile Placement area and you "lock" it, then this widget will NOT be available to Page Owners for placing on the Page. If you have placed this widget in the Page Profile Placement area and you "lock" it, then Page Owners will NOT be able to remove it or drag-n-drop it.
Visit your Insights Sayfa: If you have NOT placed this widget in the Sayfa Profile Placement area and you "lock" it, then this widget will NOT be available to Sayfa Owners for placing on the Sayfa. If you have placed this widget in the Sayfa Profile Placement area and you "lock" it, then Sayfa Owners will NOT be able to remove it or drag-n-drop it.

From the Global Settings of this plugin, you have allowed Sayfa Owners to be able to arrange, add and remove widgets from the profile of their Sayfalar. However, you still have control over what Sayfa Profile widgets should be available to Sayfa Owners, which widgets they should NOT be able to remove, and which ones they should be able to remove. If you have added a new plugin on your site, and would like its widget to be shown on Sayfa Profiles and NOT be removable by Sayfa Owners, then you can drop that widget into Sayfa Profile below. If you would like to show an announcement, or any HTML content on Sayfa Profiles, and NOT allow Sayfa Owners to be able to remove it, then you can do that as well below. If there is a widget coming on profiles of Sayfalar of your site that you want to be removed, then you can do that below; and many more such actions. If you drop a widget from a different plugin into the Sayfa Profile, then Sayfa Owners will NOT be able to remove it or drag-n-drop it. If you "lock" a Sayfa Profile widget that has NOT been placed in the Sayfa Profile Placement area, then that widget will NOT be available to Sayfa Owners for placing on the Sayfa. If you "lock" a Sayfa Profile widget that has been placed in the Sayfa Profile Placement area, then Sayfa Owners will NOT be able to remove it or drag-n-drop it.
NOTE: If you have placed "Ad Campaign" or "Html Block" on this sayfa, then once you click on the "Save Changes" link, you will neither be able to change the position nor edit that block. So, if you want to do so, you will have to remove that block from the Sayfa and save changes and then place it again from the Available Blocks.

Visit your Insights Page: This widget forms the Info tab on the Page Profile and displays the information of the Page. It should be placed in the Tabbed Blocks area of the Page Profile. You may enter content for this section from the Edit Info and Profile Info sections of the Page Dashboard.
Visit your Insights Sayfa: This widget forms the Info tab on the Sayfa Profile and displays the information of the Sayfa. It should be placed in the Tabbed Blocks area of the Sayfa Profile. You may enter content for this section from the Edit Info and Profile Info sections of the Sayfa Dashboard.

Visit your Insights Page: This widget forms the Map tab on the Page Profile. It displays the map showing the Page position as well as the location details of the page. It should be placed in the Tabbed Blocks area of the Page Profile. Location details can be entered from the Location section of the Dashboard. Note that this feature will be available to you based on your Page\'s Package and your Member Level.
Visit your Insights Sayfa: This widget forms the Map tab on the Sayfa Profile. It displays the map showing the Sayfa position as well as the location details of the sayfa. It should be placed in the Tabbed Blocks area of the Sayfa Profile. Location details can be entered from the Location section of the Dashboard. Note that this feature will be available to you based on your Sayfa\'s Package and your Member Level.
